{"tid":2500240,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"OH MY GIRL Arin 擔任內衣廣告模特未實穿！引網兩派爭論 「毫無意義」 V.S 「有何不好」","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T14:48:24.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"094e26f4547ee40541c0372c3f03c209ef68425b","tid":2500240,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"本月 19日，在韓網社群平台上出現了「 OH MY GIRL Arin BYC 內衣廣告畫報.jpg」的文章，卻意外引起網友們的爭論，成為了熱門話題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/04/22/550_1565289_1619069108.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F550_1565289_1619069108.webp&h=f3a6b696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍攝的畫報中，可以看到內衣幾乎是掛在衣架上或盒子裡，而 Arin 在一旁襬出姿勢。 這與一般內衣模特兒親自穿著內衣展示商品的其他廣告截然不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/04/22/550_1565284_1619069089.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F550_1565284_1619069089.webp&h=80d53b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爲了強調 Arin 開朗可愛的國民妹妹形象，似乎有意地儘量在廣告中減少了裸露。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/04/22/550_1565287_1619070676.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F550_1565287_1619070676.webp&h=a944cb8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而這次 Arin 作為廣告代言人的商品，除了內衣還包含了睡衣， Arin 則只在睡衣商品的部分實際穿著拍攝，讓不少網友表示似乎很「矛盾」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/04/22/550_1565286_1619069096.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F550_1565286_1619069096.webp&h=7a60e92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友們紛紛留言稱：「太保守了」、「內衣模特不穿內衣合理嗎」、「女生們好像也會覺得爲什麼沒有試穿照」、「這不是大家希望的吧」、「這樣還有當模特兒的意義嗎」等留言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/04/22/550_1565288_1619069104.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F550_1565288_1619069104.webp&h=70f57ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反，也有不少粉絲替 Arin 說道：「真的什麼都可以拿出來講」、「 甚至還有連產品功能、設計都沒出鏡的形象廣告，這有什麼問題啊」，「這樣反而看起來很好」、「有人規定內衣廣告只能穿內衣嗎」、「也有男模特兒代言衛生棉啊」、「睡衣廣告很可愛啊，為什麼這麼多人不滿」等意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/04/22/550_1565290_1619069477.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F04%2F22%2F550_1565290_1619069477.webp&h=d8f2a016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 OH MY GIRL Arin 今年將續約 BYC 專屬模特，持續展開活動。"},{"pid":"1fa19a865dd9638998a75985ab88f36082dfcc20","tid":2500240,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc0e669b6a98f8ebe53a9884315dc9674fe231a","tid":2500240,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"支持..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f40180a1ee14e40fa2183688bc9f05d91ccb9e","tid":2500240,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bc0e669b6a98f8ebe53a9884315dc9674fe231a","tid":2500240,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"支持..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"支持著上身"},{"pid":"4a02810b3961371eb364974d0a3c0116f4fe228c","tid":2500240,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86f40180a1ee14e40fa2183688bc9f05d91ccb9e","tid":2500240,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bc0e669b6a98f8ebe53a9884315dc9674fe231a","tid":2500240,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"支持..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"支持著上身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:04:28.000Z","ms